FBIS3-9447 "dreeu058_a_94004" FBIS-EEU-94-058 Document Type:Daily Report 24 Mar 1994 ALBANIA Group Protests Arrest of Kosovar Publicist AU2403190894 Tirana TVSH Television Network in Albanian 1735 GMT 24 Mar 94 AU2403190894 Tirana TVSH Television Network Language: Albanian Article Type:BFN [Text] The Albanian Helsinki Committee [KShH] raises its voice of protest over the arrest by Serbian police of Kosovar publicist and writer Shuaip Beqiri, who is also editor-in-chief of the weekly independent FORUMI, which is published in Prishtina. The KShH appeals to international institutions to seriously assess the dangerous escalation of violence in Kosova, as this escalation foreshadows new tragedies that can happen in the Balkans and the wider region.
